To update files on the sourceforge site or work with the site

Via sftp
===========

sftp chrismorgan@web.sourceforge.net
cd /home/groups/s/sh/sharppcap/htdocs/

Currently index.php contains php to redirect users to mediawiki:

<?php header("Location: http://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/sharppcap"); exit; ?>


Via ssh
===========
https://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/sourceforge/wiki/Shell%20service

- Create the shell via:
  ssh chrismorgan,sharppcap@shell.sourceforge.net create

- Log in via the shell
  ssh chrismorgan,sharppcap@shell.sourceforge.net

- Change directory to the proper directory:
  cd /home/groups/s/sh/sharppcap/htdocs/

